      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.HcYYyiTFKmgVu94h]{Fixer}</p>\n<p>Among criminals, your name is spoken in a respectful tone. Lower the DC of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.GcVVfpQ79HdcMqBt]{Bluff}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.1tzIBDaDAO4hmX5C]{Diplomacy}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.6fqgiVqlA7u9jS4i]{Intimidate} checks you attempt against criminals who know of you by 5. In addition, as a full action, you can attempt an Intimidate check to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.6fqgiVqlA7u9jS4i#demoralize]{demoralize} all foes within 60 feet. The DC of this check is the highest DC to demoralize any one of those foes. If you succeed, each foe is @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.nywSVEeDvp1bk7L3]{shaken} for 1 round plus 1 round for every 5 by which your check result exceeds the DC.</p>"
